    "content": "---\nurl: https://www.wptripura.nic.in/tnp.html\ndepth: 5\nscore: 0\ncrawled_at: 2026-07-11T20:41:46.051520Z\n---\n| |\n| --- |\n\n|\n| **The Institute** |\n| --- |\n| [Principal's Desk](https://www.wptripura.nic.in/principal.html)\n\n|\n| The Departments |\n| [Information Technology](https://www.wptripura.nic.in/itcs.html)\n\n|\n| Other Activities |\n| [NSS Cell](https://www.wptripura.nic.in/nss.html)\n\n|\n|\n\n**[ NEWSLETTERS](https://www.wptripura.nic.in/Newsletter.html) [ ](https://www.wptripura.nic.in/Newsletter.html)\n\nScholarships** |\n|\n\n| **\nTRAINING & PLACEMENT CELL**\n\n|\n| --- |\n|\n**Vission:-**\n* The Training & Placement Cell envisages student empowerment and career building through technical education integrated with personality development and professional etiquette.\n\n|\n|\n**Mission:-**\n\n* To provide placements and internships to all the interested passing-out candidates of the Institute.\n* To organize Training programs, Workshops, Seminars, Industry interactions, Industrial trainings, and visits to prominent Institutes of excellence and industries for development of desired skills essential for suitable job profile/higher education/self-employment/entrepreneurial projects.\n* To co-ordinate for conducting Faculty Development Programs (FDP) and Staff Development Programs (SDP)for overall improvement in students’ performance through the skill development of the faculties and staffs.\n* To encourage the students in the Entrepreneurship Development area with a view to make them Job-Creators.\n\n|\n|\n**Chairman:-**\n* Dr. Tirtharaj Sen, Principal\n\n|\n|\n**Training and Placement Officer:-**\n* Dr. Manash C Das, Lecturer (Sr. Scale), MLT Dept.\n\n\"**Link to provide Track Record of Passout Students of Women's Polytechnic** \"\nLink: |\n|\n\n| **\nCONSTITUTION OF TRAINING & PLACEMENT CELL\n**\n|\n| --- |\n| **Information Technology** |\n| 01 | Faculty Co-Ordinator\n|\n* Dr. Manash C Das\n* Mobile: 8258837906\n* Email id:manashmbt@gmail.com\n\n|\n| 02 | Student Co-Ordinator\n|\n* Roshni Datta Choudhury\n* Roll no.: 31/IT/19/10\n* Mobile: 7629039560 (WhatsApp),7005767262\n* Email id: roshnidattachoudhury@gmail.com\n\n|\n| **Fashion Technology** |\n| 01 | Faculty Co-Ordinator\n|\n* Sutapa Saha\n* Mobile: 9856686740\n* Email id:stpsaha2@gmail.com\n\n|\n| 02 | Student Co-Ordinator\n|\n* Aradhana Shil\n* Roll no.: 31/FT/20/01\n* Mobile: 8794569144\n* Email id: aradhanashil15@gmail.com\n\n|\n| **Medical Lab Technology** |\n| 01 | Faculty Co-Ordinator\n|\n* Rajasree Debbarma\n* Mobile: 7005977738\n* Email id:rajasreedb@gmail.com\n\n|\n| 02 | Student Co-Ordinator\n|\n* Anamika Debnath\n* Roll No.: 31/MT/19/11\n* Mobile: 7642941016 (whatsApp),7005835582, 8730040418\n* Email id: anamikadebnath1234@gmail.com\n\n|\n| **Computer Science and Technology** |\n| 01 | Faculty Co-Ordinator\n|\n* Sheela Debbarma\n* Mobile: 8731042662\n* Email id: sheeladebbarma.2662@gmail.com\n\n|\n| 02 | Student Co-Ordinator\n|\n* Debankita Mukhapadhay\n* Roll no.: 31/CS/19/11\n* Mobile: 8259940053(WhatApp),8259039585\n* Email id:20122000bm@gmail.com\n\n|\n| **Electronics and Telecommunication Engineering** |\n| 01 | Faculty Co-Ordinator\n|\n* Bappaditya Sarkar\n* Mobile: 7005243450\n* Email id: bappastar@gmail.com\n\n|\n| 02 | Student Co-Ordinator\n|\n* Chameli Reang\n* Roll no.: 31/ET/19/20\n* Mob: 8974505049\n* Email id: chamelireang4638@gmail.com\n\n|\n\n|\n|\n\n|",
